title: Eight exchanges handle 90% of crypto trading, Kaiko data shows
description: Kaiko’s report comes in the wake of the year’s biggest decline in crypto trading volume numbers. Per CCData, the combined spot and derivative trading volumes in August fell by more than 11% to $2.09 trillion.
